flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Periodic data refresh from SAP S/4HANA.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Collect and cleanse indirect spend data.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Perform spend cube analysis to identify cost-saving opportunities.]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: AutoML - Analyze indirect demand and consumption patterns.]
  N3 --> N4[PB: Process Builder - Execute tail spend management programs.]
  N4 --> N5[PB: UI Screens - Track and report on realized savings.]
  N5 --> N6{Decision: Identify and execute cost-saving opportunities from indirect spend data.}
  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Realized savings and improved EBITDA through optimized indirect spend management.]
  N6 -->|Low savings realization| B1[Adjust optimization strategies and re-run analysis.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Improved savings realization.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N6 -->|High demand variability| B2[Increase frequency of demand analysis.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: More accurate demand forecasting.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N6 -->|Supplier consolidation issues| B3[Engage with suppliers for negotiation.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Enhanced supplier relationships and cost savings.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]